  "detailed_description": "<h1>CHECK OUT OUR UPCOMING GAME</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/427ee429bc64a2c9993ac06057a5e3a6.avif?t=1693878202\" width=520 height=180 /></span><br><br><strong>Clean up all the grounds by controlling the cute cleaning robot A-12!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/2b4d57910148593fb5bdc06662253612.poster.avif?t=1693878202\" width=480 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/2b4d57910148593fb5bdc06662253612.webm?t=1693878202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/2b4d57910148593fb5bdc06662253612.mp4?t=1693878202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Vacuum everything such as leaves, twigs, or even cans!<br> <br>Please try to carry the big objects when it’s hard to vacuum.<br> <br>You can clean more efficiently by upgrading your robot.<br> <br>You can obtain cute and cool loadouts!<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/1af3926366710c60ad464f4924e2ffcc.poster.avif?t=1693878202\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/1af3926366710c60ad464f4924e2ffcc.webm?t=1693878202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/1af3926366710c60ad464f4924e2ffcc.mp4?t=1693878202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>Gain true satisfaction by viewing the tidiness of the place where you just cleaned!<br>There is no competition or pressure when you clean. Enjoy cleaning while you are relaxed and comfortable.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/aca08190c18b39e00d0f33da82226072.avif?t=1693878202\" width=520 height=180 /></span><br><br>Introduction of Cream<br> <br>Cream is a grassroots company from Seoul, South Korea who develop indie games.<br>Our team is made up of three individuals.<br>We would like to further improve and introduce better quality games.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/427ee429bc64a2c9993ac06057a5e3a6.avif?t=1693878202\" width=520 height=180 /></span><br><br><strong>Clean up all the grounds by controlling the cute cleaning robot A-12!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/2b4d57910148593fb5bdc06662253612.poster.avif?t=1693878202\" width=480 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/2b4d57910148593fb5bdc06662253612.webm?t=1693878202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/2b4d57910148593fb5bdc06662253612.mp4?t=1693878202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Vacuum everything such as leaves, twigs, or even cans!<br> <br>Please try to carry the big objects when it’s hard to vacuum.<br> <br>You can clean more efficiently by upgrading your robot.<br> <br>You can obtain cute and cool loadouts!<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/1af3926366710c60ad464f4924e2ffcc.poster.avif?t=1693878202\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/1af3926366710c60ad464f4924e2ffcc.webm?t=1693878202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/1af3926366710c60ad464f4924e2ffcc.mp4?t=1693878202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br>Gain true satisfaction by viewing the tidiness of the place where you just cleaned!<br>There is no competition or pressure when you clean. Enjoy cleaning while you are relaxed and comfortable.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687150/extras/aca08190c18b39e00d0f33da82226072.avif?t=1693878202\" width=520 height=180 /></span><br><br>Introduction of Cream<br> <br>Cream is a grassroots company from Seoul, South Korea who develop indie games.<br>Our team is made up of three individuals.<br>We would like to further improve and introduce better quality games.",
